ratings.en: Sô, ano toki wa mô, suicchi ga haittetan ja nai kanâ
Sôzô o koete wakari aeterutte, kanjiru toki ga aru. Gyaku no toki mo ôi kedone
Zutto mae kara shikumareteta, sonna deaitte, shinziru?
Chûningu ga atta tameshi ga nai. Motto Ryôkô na basho ga aru to omotteshimau
Mitsukaranaimono ga, mawari o kowasu. Soko ni nai kara, te no uchiyou ga nai
